News.headline: Match Officials FA Youth Challenge Cup: Dagenham & Redbridge FC (Under 19s) v Cheshunt FC (Under 19s)
News.page_title: Match Officials FA Youth Challenge Cup: Dagenham & Redbridge FC (Under 19s) v Cheshunt FC (Under 19s)
News.URL_keywords: Match Officials FA Youth Challenge Cup: Daggers v Cheshunt FC
News.short_description: Thursday's referee for the Dagenham & Redbridge FC (Under 19s) FA Youth Challenge Cup home game against Cheshunt FC (Under 19s) has been named as Kadir Nazif
News.description:
The two assistants have been named as Gary Caley and Christopher Noble.

Ticket will be available on the turnstiles only.

Ticket Prices:
Adults: £4
Concessions/Juniors: £1
